@startuml artifact_passing
title Artifact Passing Pattern Between Workflow Steps

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #e3f2fd
    BorderColor #1565c0
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #fff3e0
    BorderColor #e65100
}

rectangle "Step 1: Preprocessing" as step1 {
    component "Container" as c1
}

database "MinIO\n(S3 Storage)" as minio

rectangle "Step 2: Training" as step2 {
    component "Container" as c2
}

c1 -right-> minio : **1.** Write output\n(/tmp/output/data.csv)
minio -right-> c2 : **2.** Mount input\n(/tmp/input/data.csv)

note bottom of minio
  **No direct pod-to-pod communication**
  
  • Step 1 writes to local path
  • Argo uploads to S3 automatically
  • Argo downloads to Step 2
  • Pods are ephemeral and isolated
end note

note top of step1
  Pod created,
  executes,
  terminates
end note

note top of step2
  Created only after
  Step 1 succeeds
end note

@enduml
